<h2 id="Paleontology">Paleontology<a class="anchor-link" href="#Paleontology">&#182;</a></h2>The study of fossils: their age, method of formation, and evolutionary significance.
<h2 id="Biostratigraphy">Biostratigraphy<a class="anchor-link" href="#Biostratigraphy">&#182;</a></h2>The branch of Paleontology where the identification of fossils found within sedimentary rock strata is used as a method of determining the relative geologic age(dating) of the rock.

