<h1 id="Data-augmentation-using-transformation">Data augmentation using transformation<a class="anchor-link" href="#Data-augmentation-using-transformation">&#182;</a></h1>As the goal is to identify fossils from new images, we can already augment our training dataset by using 
cropping, flipping, rotating and adding random noise. There are more advanced transformation technique available 
which we will use in future if necessary.

